<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412b4a7f4452e46de50e82981fd7befe365da0d4","tid":290222,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:41:34.000Z","msg":"2噸既車有轆，姐係幾多G力可以推郁？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申，一腳踩郁5.5噸輕型貨車"},{"pid":"d2b021da2634d4e76087bb2e18396e6b3d2d59c8","tid":290222,"uid":121653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:43:59.000Z","msg":"真唔撚真阿"},{"pid":"0e846d973317183666088b5d4302756a2a21f68f","tid":290222,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-frt3-1.cdninstagram.com/t51.2885-15/s640x640/sh0.08/e35/14591158_1712925312359324_878110294209986560_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-frt3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fs640x640%2Fsh0.08%2Fe35%2F14591158_1712925312359324_878110294209986560_n.jpg&h=55c2310c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62adc4a6b56cdb834d3dfcfdcbad70c6dfcf413f","tid":290222,"uid":53705,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:50:16.000Z","msg":"解放軍 其實同清末時期既清軍一樣<br />\n<br />\n成日吹到自己刀槍不入, 心口碎大石咁<br />\n但同外國軍隊打仗, 就會兵敗如山倒<br />\n<br />\n不過當鎮壓自己人民果陣, 又會戰鬥力快速上升<br />\n就好似打 太平天國既城市,  一路打一路屠城"},{"pid":"7bff826e0e2bab22b0b6d96e4751fbaa2056193c","tid":290222,"uid":57787,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"推車項目價目表2017<br />\n<br />\n行車速度 - 港幣<br />\n1km/h - $1000<br />\n2km/h - $2000<br />\n3km/h - $3000<br />\n4km/h - $4000<br />\n5km/h - $5000<br />\n<br />\n**康師傅特惠套餐(坐駕駛席旁+泡麵+飲料) - $10000**<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038fadca8a5725edad4944fc36896a90b5b1445f","tid":290222,"uid":56432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:52:37.000Z","msg":"越嚟越北韓化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif