。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n整係演習同做下火燭鬼已經射到成地都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a980bc80ee2f49e4f94e5984ab68c999273f8a","tid":290222,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>M到都要做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/083655_078c5f0ec25834a7ace221909bd30ffd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F083655_078c5f0ec25834a7ace221909bd30ffd.jpg&h=26e00859&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n任何任務都要做，只要領導出聲"},{"pid":"3babcf2021489bdac19ce404d11060e01a0e914b","tid":290222,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:29:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔難<br />\n有推過就知<br />\n貴價車會仲易推<br />\n因零件間摩擦力少</blockquote><br />\n咁個架一定係德國貨"},{"pid":"33abcc94bc9add19d43127cb87c66eb27fbf77e7","tid":290222,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:29:16.000Z","msg":"我反而想知佢係邊度推姐，個個都推一次，都無人見過，香港有咁大地方俾佢地推車？"},{"pid":"8ab1efc97bd8574862bbc58cc790e75fff3e3d47","tid":290222,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:36:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2017-06/19/1121169034_14978440570611n.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.xinhuanet.com%2Fpolitics%2F2017-06%2F19%2F1121169034_14978440570611n.gif&h=a49a3e4b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咩姐呀係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066270ffa70b7e98be4c999843e136b88d8d2c8c","tid":290222,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"